  ..$ : chr [1:6] "A" "B" "C" "D" ...
 num [1:1200] 8636 7040 9275 4821 2475 ...

Somehow the structure is lost. 

This happens, if I mix matrix and data.frame data, and doesn?t, if I use only matrices. The man page defines matrix-like objects, 
