docker run -p 8787:8787 bioconductor/devel_core2

After doing so, navigating to:

http://127.0.0.1:8787/

will open up Rstudio running on R-devel with core bioc-devel packages
installed.

Full details are here: http://bioconductor.org/help/docker/

